[Student "S"]
{SOUTH, with 9 points and a 6-card suit, knows they should play in \Ss. 
The question is: how high? 

SOUTH transfers NORTH to \Ss, then invites by raising to 3\S.

NORTH has only two trumps, (good ones, admittedly), but she has a maximum 17 point hand. 
So she bids the \S game.}

