[Student "S"]
{EAST, with a 5-card AND a 4-card Major first uses Stayman.

WEST denies a 4-card Major, so EAST realizes that \Ss are out. 
He then bids \Hs, promising five of them.

WEST not only has three \Hs, she also has 17 points so 
she bids 4\H.}

